I am against:

Tinkering with blobs in order to try and extract more L1 fees out of rollups.

I am for:

Improving the blob fee market to make it more reactive to changes in demand and reduce the lagtime to price discovery.

Let the blobs do their job of scaling Ethereum!

ENS is the industry standard for blockchains as a whole
